Package org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom

Class TagElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.ASTNode
      • org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.AbstractTagElement
        • org.eclipse.jdt.core.dom.TagElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDocElement
    public final class TagElement
extends AbstractTagElement
    AST node for a tag within a doc comment. Tag elements nested within another tag element are called inline doc tags. 
     TagElement:
     [ @ Identifier ] { DocElement }
     {tagProperty = tagValue}
 DocElement:
     TextElement
     Name
     MethodRef
     MemberRef
     { TagElement }
    Since:
    3.0
    See Also:
    Javadoc
    Restriction:
    This class is not intended to be instantiated by clients.
